{"tid":1547652,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢排文宣做咩停左手腳咁？好需要大家全力推動","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:48:22.000Z","uid":81236,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2b6fa567dd3fb9d158e7a895a89f18cee0b703","tid":1547652,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"大家係對831同埋咁多手足離去惋惜既同時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">請唔好忘記要繼承佢地既遺願</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然未必個個都可以上前線<br />\n<br />\n但一定個每個人都可以為文宣出一分力<br />\n<br />\n好多連儂牆同埋外國文宣都需要大家親力親為<br />\n<br />\n唔係上fb ig㩒一下share就完成<br />\n<br />\n明白大家返工返學會好攰<br />\n<br />\n但為左香港人，我地唔可以停低<br />\n<br />\n我都攰，但連前線為香港人出生入死未話攰既時候<br />\n<br />\n我<br />\n<br />\n作為一個香港人，沒有停下來的理由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特別黎緊人權法案等等接住黎<br />\n<br />\n好需要大家一齊出多一分力<br />\n<br />\n多你一個未必多好多<br />\n<br />\n但少你一個就真係係少一個<br />\n<br />\n香港人既成敗，就係欠你既積極參與<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb8dcd538462594fe9011f1c22f697ca64dd7ca","tid":1547652,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2icuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=454ff560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/twitter4HK</a>"},{"pid":"83ecc2e60d6fffb0859225dbde5c17563fe21e36","tid":1547652,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2f8e0d8c1db7ce1e8a8045da0ac68eae05740c8","tid":1547652,"uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:35:15.000Z","msg":"文宣組係你下屬？"},{"pid":"293563216b7c736c4c7c4847ec8a41a0a794a210","tid":1547652,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06